data.title: SHODO SUPER Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger 2 & 3 Sets Official Images Revealed
data.meta_description: Here are the official images of the SHODO SUPER Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger 2 & 3 sets.
data.text:
Premium Bandai posted the official images of the SHODO SUPER Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger 2 and 3 sets from the Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger series.

â€‹Released as part of the show's 10th anniversary, this set features each figure standing 100mm tall, and are the second and third batches of the SHODO SUPER Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger line as these two sets completes the entire team.

The SHODO SUPER Zyuden Sentai Kyoryuger 2 comes with Kyoryu Gold, Kyoryu Silver, and Kyoryu Violet. That said, the set comes with Zandar Thunder, Gaburivolver (x1 open, x1 closed), the bayonet version of the folded Gaburicalibur for Kyoryu Violet, GigaGaburevolver (x1 open, x1 closed), Feather Edge, and a set of interchangeable hands.

In addition, though not included in this set, this set comes with accessories for the SHODO SUPER Kyoryu Red Carnival's Carnival Biting Change, namely for Kyoryu Red Samba Carnival and Kyoryu Red Western Carnival. This Premium Bandai web exclusive set cost 7,975 yen, and is set for a March 2025 release.
